{"tid":2204044,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"網民太古廣場悼念墮樓示威者 警方在場戒備","createTime":"2020-09-15T18:30:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T18:30:07.000Z","uid":224066,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"eef7a9448ff5ff996a2bd2b9149a1a70b3f95dd2","tid":2204044,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T18:30:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/3lwb0K4ALmhlrYEmgSttwA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/onccinstantnews.com/3f5b110295fdb08bdbf5cb1039407297\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F3lwb0K4ALmhlrYEmgSttwA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2F3f5b110295fdb08bdbf5cb1039407297&h=c4f3ae6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有網民發起今晚(15日)在金鐘太古廣場外，悼念去年6月15日在上址從高處墮下離世的反修例示威者梁凌杰。晚上7時，數名市民到場聚集，其中人稱「Lunch哥」的姓李中六男學生亦有現身，他手持鮮花並舉起手勢。不過，警方在活動開始前，已派出多輛警車在太古廣場一帶戒備，一批警員亦在場截查多人。其後，有市民擺放燃點的蠟燭及鮮花在花槽進行悼念。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/LOc7ywr61FBrNUqLFAkgxg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/onccinstantnews.com/8951a3d9512580259d581c6969053f7b\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FLOc7ywr61FBrNUqLFAkgxg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2F8951a3d9512580259d581c6969053f7b&h=ad268f6f&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}